Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.53,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:14.17,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}僕らの願いが届くまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.06,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}大事なものまた一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.68,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}モノクロの空へと消える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:34.47,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隠したキズ冷たく震え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.85,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分の居場所を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:46.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}常識に従うこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:51.38,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}どうしようもできないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.58,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}壊していきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:01:03.13,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}閉ざしたココロ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:10.58,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:16.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分さえも見失いそうになって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.15,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}曖昧な答えはイラナイ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:26.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}確かな今　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲傷的連鎖之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:14.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在我們的願望實現之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}又一件珍貴的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}消失在黑白的空中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:34.47,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隱藏的傷痕在發冷顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去找尋我的容身之處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:46.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在這個遵循常識的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:51.38,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想打破無可救藥的桎梏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}按自己的意志自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:01:03.13,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}封閉的心靈正發出吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:10.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲傷的連鎖之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:16.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我們幾乎快要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.15,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不需要曖昧的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:26.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只需去追尋真切的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======TEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國那幫傢伙 真會蠻幹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂來 埃米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的哥哥 這種程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張起彈幕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃米爾 振作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶他離開這裡為好 在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在帶埃米爾走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍的安裝進程如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 即將完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成後能第一時間撤離蘭蒂格瑞絲城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓加利亞人入侵就麻煩了 盡早完工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 卡爾·奧薩·瓦魯特少尉看到了沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍部隊情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在確認中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為事出突然 其他部隊也亂作一團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應急包紮完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 出血量很大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作 埃米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我們不是說好要一起回家鄉的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會沒事的 還是男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說喪氣話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉魯高大人你也受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點擦傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是戰艦突然衝進城來 又是突然交火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能拖延戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據情況也可能發生近距離戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不是要去救艾麗西婭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 現在不是說這種話的場合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的陸地戰艦突擊前一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吉蘭達約發生大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 那艾麗西婭已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說不吉利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要專注於眼前的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的手開闢出自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則 沒臉去見艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莎 埃米爾就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 把他們一個不留全部幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備就緒 隨時能夠啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等 聽說卡爾被殺了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為違抗吾的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你殺的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 哪怕是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽敢頂撞的話 也不會手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多厚的裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐個摧毀它的炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用彈幕拉近距離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要移動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們攻擊造成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大塊頭根本沒受什麼損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們打算後退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家撤退到市中心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷似艾麗西婭使用的女武神長矛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是女武神的聖槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 古代遺產被封印在這座城堡的塔樓中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪長久以來無人能知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台Merlot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為再現聖槍神力而設計的陸地戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神力？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把聖槍是達魯庫斯之災中使用過的傳說之物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神人利用聖槍的神力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊敗達魯庫斯人 迫使他們降伏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降伏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神人不是救世主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神人篡改了歷史而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們侵略了這片由達魯庫斯人掌管的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神人使用聖槍的力量將它據為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後歪曲史實進行傳承
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷史只為勝利者而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖槍 炮擊準備開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試射 瞄準8點方向丘陵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們先睹為快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊準備開始 向8點方向轉舵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標8點方向 丘陵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中目標
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動用能量不足20%
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20%的話只有這種程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能強求了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知加利亞軍士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止無謂的反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的主力已經在吉蘭達約遭到全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對我們的陸地戰艦Merlot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 艾麗西婭果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有向她道歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 現在不是為這種事傷心的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:10:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們也正受到死亡的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止無意義的流血 立即投降
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍 立即投降
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 這種時候就放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們確實不是那東西的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別傻了 真打算乖乖投降嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無非戰鬥到死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想摧毀我們的戰鬥意志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有必要動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不相信的話 還有誰相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放棄 直到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生還是死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這分界線的前後徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利 失敗 逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些單詞 此時此刻失去了意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存下來 生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是唯一的願望 為之祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭 活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止仍沒有投降者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗反而更猛烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖槍的能量呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充填已經結束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時可以炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始壓制城池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續等也是浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 耶格爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此追求力量又能如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽爾貝莉亞在吉蘭達約犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著那個叫艾麗西婭的女武神人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和加利亞的主力部隊陪葬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亞實際上已經被征服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你似乎還另有目的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回答我一個問題 耶格爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的祖國被格雷戈爾攻陷 淪為帝國的附屬國
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你不也利用吾爬上今天的地位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今為何又疑惑？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所知 我為爭取祖國費拉爾德的獨立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安 把所有賭注都壓在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有軍事力量就能奪回祖國
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有軍事力量能夠保衛祖國
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看看現在 馬克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過這次攻略加利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反而糊塗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜拋棄忠實部下追求力量的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和熱愛祖國 珍惜戰友的那些加利亞義勇軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護事物時需要的 到底是何種姿態？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有力量在手 進可攻退可守
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說 你尋找聖槍不是為了征服加利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初就是為了那種目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜得沒錯 正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為把那可憎的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我的父親和兄長一起埋葬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾要超越帝國皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為女武神之王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有聖槍的力量就能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊準備開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是蘭蒂格瑞絲城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 這次打算射這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果瞄準的是這座城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始逃也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後都不要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當真嗎 馬克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它摧毀一切的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難保不會再現真實版的達魯庫斯之災
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在災厄果真降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾將與這命運奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量充填完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始倒數計時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方有人出現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 是艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還活著 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告 炮擊前受到不明攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量對沖消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的女武神人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家去掩護艾麗西婭 走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:17:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 大家要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標依舊健在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉蘭達約的戰鬥中受創未癒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還無法隨心所欲控制這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽爾貝莉亞也曾有過類似情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖槍能量充填完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為保護至愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的攻擊造成第四炮塔重創
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即前往修復
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時回收女武神人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你打算把那女孩怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有更多的力量太過危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 還打算重演賽爾貝莉亞的悲劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過了 如果有心妨礙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你也不會手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我也無法繼續贊同你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選擇和你分道揚鑣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 太可惜了 耶格爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去救艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可能服從這種命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛說過不許偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉來晚了 維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七小隊 現在開始前往營救艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許他們靠近 開火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我們 艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:46.11,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}悲しすぎる瞳が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:52.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}この空を映す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:22:01.17,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}掛ける言葉がわからずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:07.02,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただ　星を数えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:12.74,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独で居る世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:19.52,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}得意なはずだと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:26.03,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}振りかえる日々　あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:32.46,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}探していた　きみをひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:39.10,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}もしもいま許されるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:45.79,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}きみのことだけ想うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:53.68,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}忘れたくない悲しみならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:23:01.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただそれが　それだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:07.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}そう  ひとつの願い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:46.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}太過悲傷的眼眸
